Subject: Price Quotation for Uniformed Security Guard Service

We are pleased to present our comprehensive quotation for security guard services.

Our rates are inclusive of the guard's compensation and liability insurances, social security fund(SSF), training costs, recruitment processes, thorough employee screening (including criminal records checks and drug testing), uniforms and boots, as well as all other management and supervisory overheads.


Price Quotation for Uniformed Security Guard Service
S.N Guard Rank Working Hours Rate
1 Guard Supervisor - 12 Hrs. Shift - 32,500.00
2 Head Guard- 12 Hrs. Shift - 30,500.00
3 Guard - 12 Hrs. Shift - 29,500.00


Notes: 
	The about amount is negotiable.
	You will have to pay for a total of 13 monthly installments (12 regular monthly installments + 1 month Dashain Bonus for the Guard) in a year.
	
	

